> <span begin="33.542" end="34.137">doubt</span><span begin="34.137" end="34.858">s I</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">没有任何犹疑 我就这样轻装前行</span></p><p begin="36.135" end="38.658" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="36.135" end="36.313">Found</span> <span begin="36.313" end="36.453">my</span><span begin="36.453" end="36.778">self</span> <span begin="36.778" end="36.949">cros</span><span begin="36.949" end="37.119">sing</span> <span begin="37.119" end="37.418">path</span><span begin="37.418" end="37.601">s un</span><span begin="37.601" end="37.751">ex</span><span begin="37.751" end="38.207">pec</span><span begin="38.207" end="38.658">ted</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在某个意料之外的瞬间 与你相遇</span></p><p begin="38.658" end="41.562" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="38.658" end="38.846">An</span><span begin="38.846" end="39.018">d up</span> <span begin="39.018" end="39.308">clo</span><span begin="39.308" end="39.509">se I</span> <span begin="39.509" end="39.658">in</span><span begin="39.658" end="39.971">dulged</span> <span begin="39.971" end="40.118">in</span> <span begin="40.118" end="40.296">the</span> <span begin="40.296" end="40.680">mes</span><span begin="40.680" end="41.562">sage</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">靠近之后 我沉溺于你传递的一切</span></p><p begin="41.877" end="45.072" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="41.877" end="42.045">Get</span><span begin="42.045" end="42.227">ting</span> <span begin="42.227" end="42.374">lu</span><span begin="42.374" end="42.546">red in</span><span begin="42.546" end="42.689">to</span> <span begin="42.689" end="42.864">a</span> <span begin="42.864" end="43.755">false</span> <span begin="43.755" end="43.977">sense of</span> <span begin="43.977" end="44.135">se</span><span begin="44.135" end="44.440">cu</span><span begin="44.440" end="44.623">ri</span><span begin="44.623" end="45.072">ty</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">就这样 被诱入一种虚假的安心</span