相 从来没有意义</span></p><p begin="1:08.709" end="1:11.016" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:08.709" end="1:09.095">I</span> <span begin="1:09.352" end="1:09.647">can</span> <span begin="1:09.647" end="1:10.007">feel</span> <span begin="1:10.007" end="1:10.168">wi</span><span begin="1:10.168" end="1:10.622">thout</span> <span begin="1:10.622" end="1:11.016">shame</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我可以坦然地感受这一切</span></p><p begin="1:11.262" end="1:16.162" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:11.262" end="1:11.576">Even</span> <span begin="1:11.576" end="1:11.759">i</span><span begin="1:11.759" end="1:11.906">f a</span><span begin="1:11.906" end="1:12.053">fter</span> <span begin="1:12.053" end="1:12.207">re</span><span begin="1:12.207" end="1:12.522">sis</span><span begin="1:12.522" end="1:12.858">tance</span> <span begin="1:12.858" end="1:13.306">melt</span><span begin="1:13.306" end="1:13.494">s a</span><span begin="1:13.494" end="1:13.803">way</span> <span begin="1:13.803" end="1:14.206">it</span> <span begin="1:14.444" end="1:14.763">was</span> <span begin="1:14.763" end="1:15.112">not</span> <span begin="1:15.112" end="1:15.693">in</span> <span begin="1:15.693" end="1:16.162">vain</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">就算我的爱被一点点磨灭 也并非徒劳</span></p><p begin="1:16.351" end="1:22.490" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:16.351" end="1:16.687">Yes</span> <span begin="1:16.687" end="1:17.016">I</span> <span begin="1:17.016" end="1:17.638">know</span> <span begin="1:17.638" end="1:18.577">now</span> <span begin="1:18.926" end="1:19.277">that</span> <span begin="1:19.277" end="1:19.578">this</span> <span begin="1:19.578" end="1:20.166">should</span> <span begin="1:20.166" end="1:22.490">be</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我知道 这是命运使然</span></p><p begin="1:42.515" end="1:47.046" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:42.515" end="1:42.804">In</span> <span begin="1:42.804" end="1:43.802">secret</span> <span begin="1:43.802" end="1:43.970">le</span><span begin="1:43.970" end="1:44.124">t us</span> <span begin="1:44.124" end="1:44.602">ren</span><span begin="1:44.602" end="1:45.065">de</span><span begin="1:45.065" end="1:47.046">zvous</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">让我们在无人知晓处悄悄相约</span></p><p begin="1:47.625" end="1:51.658" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:47.625" end="1:47.959">With</span> <span begin="1:47.959" end="1:48.376">whis</span><span begin="1:48.376" end="1:48.901">pers</span> <span begin="1:48.901" end="1:49.046">in</span> <span begin="1:49.046" end="1:49.218">the</span> <span begin="1:49.218" end="1:50.181">after</span><span begin="1:50.181" end="1:51.658">noon</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在惬意的午后时光里轻轻耳语</span></p><p begin="1:52.733" end="1:56.670" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:52.733" end="1:53.051">Un</span><span begin="1:53.051" end="1:53.512">bur</span><span begin="1:53.512" end="1:53.986">dened</span> <span begin="1:53.986" end="1:54.153">wi</span><span begin="1:54.153" end="1:54.345">thout</span> <span begin="1:54.345" end="1:54.793">need</span> <span begin="1:54.793" end="1:55.259">for</span> <span begin="1:55.259" end="1:55.862">word</span><span begin="1:55.862" end="1:56.670">s I</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">坦白一切 无需多说什么</span></p><p begin="1:57.847" end="2:00.385" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:57.847" end="1:58.016">Found</span> <span begin="1:58.016" end="1:58.530">myself</span> <span begin="1:58.530" end="1:58.656">lon</span><span begin="1:58.656" end="1:58.838">ging</span> <span begin="1:58.838" end="1:59.139">a</span><span begin="1:59.139" end="1:59.314">fter</span> <span begin="1:59.314" end="1:59.471">your</span> <span begin="1:59.471" end="1:59.916">pre</span><span begin="1:59.916" end="2:00.385">sence</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">才发现自己早已渴望你的陪伴</span></p><p begin="2:00.385" en